  <brief_title>Comparing Patients After ESWL Treated With Ureteral Stents Versus Expulsion Therapy With Tamsulosin</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study Comparing Two Groups of Patients Undergoing ESWL Treated With Ureteral Stents Versus Expulsion Therapy With Tamsulosin</official_title>
