  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to see whether patients undergoing ESWL, for upper tract urinary
      stones between 1.5-2.0cm, may be treated by expulsion therapy(Tamsulosin) instead of
      inserting ureteral stents .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
